data.description: Welcome to your new home in Warren, MA! This residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,960 sq. ft. of living space. Nestled on 0.43 acres of scenic land, this property offers plenty of room to stretch out and explore. The lovely yard space is just waiting for your green thumb or a creative project, and it's the perfect canvas for your outdoor dreams. Plus, you'll find a convenient shed and a 1-car garage for all your storage needs. This gem has been well-maintained, and minimal repairs are needed, to make it move-in ready. A group showing is scheduled on Wednesday, November 8, 2023, from 12:30 – 1:30 pm. Home sold as is where is. All due diligence/Inspections are Buyer/Buyers agent responsibility including but not limited to Smoke certs, final water/sewer readings. "Seller" currently has the property UA to buy, sale contingent on completion of "sellers" purchase, reserves right to transfer contract.
